Meet <b>Baiba</b>, our freshest Citizen of the Week!<br><br>She lives at <a href="http://millsberry.com/home/?user=linducc"><a href='/home/?user=linducc'>82680-H Broadway Boulevard</a> in Lakeview</a> and has been a citizen since November 10, 2007. Baiba isn't one to brag so we thought we would do it for her. If you haven't noticed already- she has 29 shiny trophies! It's clear she is proud of that because she shines them once a week in a room solely dedicated to her awards. She is most proud of her Gold Skull award, which she won from Halloween last year when she dressed up as an ice cream cone. <br><br>Baiba is very generous and always invites friends over to her three-floor home with twelve gardens! Talk about a home!  Being curious and smart sure has paid off. <br><br>So if your interests include history, biology, and pop and industrial music, then you might hit it off as friends! So keep an eye out for Baiba at the Amusement Park or the Pizza Place. You might also spot her driving a big old rusty car or simply rolling on her roller skates!<br></div>
